#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:178
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"GUARD_RADIKAL\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[3]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[3]/event/choice[2]/text"
